data.description: Welcome to the Woods of Fries Mill, Washington Township's best kept secret for the 52 and fabulous set! No association fees are assessed on this age restricted community. It is a tree lined cul de sac that offers beautiful views every season of the year. This is the largest model home, featuring four bedrooms and three full baths. The fully finished walk out basement has a full bath and kitchenette. It is finished into three separate areas, divided by double doors. The main floor has a living room, kitchen with sliding doors to the deck, dining room, master bedroom and full bath. The upper level has two large bedrooms with dormers, a full bath and huge storage area over the garage. Gorgeous laminate flooring is through out the main level. All baths have ceramic tiled floors and enclosures. There are six panel doors throughout the home and generous closet space. Fresh paint and carpets cleaned mean you can move right in. The yard is tastefully landscaped and a sprinkler system is in the front and back yard.Conveniently located seconds from the Black Horse Pike. This home has everything you are looking for!
